Package klingon.webserver

Class PumpStation

java.lang.Object
klingon.webserver.Beans.PumpStation
@Entity public class PumpStation extends Object
The PumpStation class is essentially a Java Bean class, which is used to encapsulate a number of objects into a single one. Hence this class encapsulates multiple PumpStation objects into a single one, namely this class (the bean).
